  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683450/extras/032a0217a6221f4d2f45e99e3b2e84cd.poster.avif?t=1774095170\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683450/extras/032a0217a6221f4d2f45e99e3b2e84cd.webm?t=1774095170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683450/extras/032a0217a6221f4d2f45e99e3b2e84cd.mp4?t=1774095170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >LETHAL DOSE is a top-down action game inspired by HOTLINE MIAMI, DISHONORED and WHERE THE WILD THINGS ARE</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast paced one hit kill combat </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supernatural abilities: dash, telefrag, chain lightning and more </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clever enemies that can coordinate searches, patrol, flank and check corners  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built in level editor: make your own levels!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is still IN DEVELOPMENT, read the section above to learn more about Early Access.<br><br>The game's campaign currently has up to 2 hours of gameplay (depending on the player's skill level), during Early Access development this will be increased to around 10 hours of gameplay. <br><br>Steam Workshop support is coming soon, so you can play custom levels created by the community!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >THANKS, and have FUN!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683450/extras/032a0217a6221f4d2f45e99e3b2e84cd.poster.avif?t=1774095170\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683450/extras/032a0217a6221f4d2f45e99e3b2e84cd.webm?t=1774095170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1683450/extras/032a0217a6221f4d2f45e99e3b2e84cd.mp4?t=1774095170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >LETHAL DOSE is a top-down action game inspired by HOTLINE MIAMI, DISHONORED and WHERE THE WILD THINGS ARE</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast paced one hit kill combat </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supernatural abilities: dash, telefrag, chain lightning and more </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clever enemies that can coordinate searches, patrol, flank and check corners  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built in level editor: make your own levels!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is still IN DEVELOPMENT, read the section above to learn more about Early Access.<br><br>The game's campaign currently has up to 2 hours of gameplay (depending on the player's skill level), during Early Access development this will be increased to around 10 hours of gameplay. <br><br>Steam Workshop support is coming soon, so you can play custom levels created by the community!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >THANKS, and have FUN!</p>",
